	=== OSGi services with Eclipse Equinox
			 This tutorial explains the usage of OSGi services primary
				focusing on the usage of declarative services.
				Eclipse Equinox is
				used as an
				stand-alone OSGi
				server. For
				this tutorial Eclipse 4.4
				(Luna) is
				used.
			
		
	
